dct_title_s: Military operations in China up to February 22, 1938
dct_description_sm: Legend shows boundaries, Great Wall, railroads, rivers, roads, battle fronts.
Flag illustrations, arrows moving out from bases of operation (Taiwan, Shanghai, Bohai Sea).
